session-appended 2026-05-21 expl-demo follow-up #8 (HEAD cc4a1cb
  session-0006 deferred + uncommitted xtask/client.ts diff). Diff
  hoists `RunRecord` from frontend hand-rolled `interface RunRecord
  { id; started_at_ms; finished_at_ms; status; wall_clock_ms;
  succeeded; inconclusive; failed }` (client.ts:109-118 OLD) into
  `nyctos-types::run::RunRecord` (run.rs:21-36) with
  `#[derive(Serialize, Deserialize, TS)]`; xtask `render()` now
  registers it (xtask/src/main.rs:117) so types.gen.ts ships the
  wire shape `{ id, started_at, finished_at, status,
  triggered_by, git_ref, parent_run_id, wall_clock_ms,
  total_ai_spend_usd_micros }` (types.gen.ts:162). Two structural
  changes simultaneously: (a) THREE operator-internal fields newly
  emitted to every `/api/v1/runs[?status=]` + `/api/v1/runs/:id`
  response that previously only carried the seven-field summary
  shape; (b) the type now derives `Deserialize` and is published
  from the shared types crate — same #78/#79/#80-class latent
  surface (Deserialize hoist without per-field validators) at a
  THIRD type, with sinks distinct from RepoSource / GitAuth.
  Pre-existing findings #1-#80 still apply unchanged. One new
  finding appended below: #81 RUNRECORD_HOIST_WIDENS_WIRE_SHAPE_AND
  _OPENS_BUDGET_DESERIALISE_FORGERY. Total: 81 findings.

